column8: [4_SAQ] 1. I will be able to achieve most of the goals that I have set for myself.
column9: [5_SAQ] 2. When facing difficult tasks I am certain that I will accomplish them.
column10: [6_SAQ] 3. In general I think that I can obtain outcomes that are important to me.
column11: [7_SAQ] 4. I believe I can succeed at most any endeavor to which I set my mind.
column12: [8_SAQ] 5. I will be able to successfully overcome many challenges.
column13: [9_SAQ] 6. I am confident that I can perform effectively on many different tasks.
column14: [10_SAQ] 7. Compared to other people I can do most tasks very well.
column15: [11_SAQ] 8. Even when things are tough I can perform quite well.
